	"nodes":[
		{"id":"c46ffba7bda32fb8","type":"text","text":"SOFTSKILL PROJECT\n","x":-467,"y":-253,"width":250,"height":60},
		{"id":"8da379e8574627cd","type":"text","text":"## **1.2  Goals**\n\n1.      Admin can create courses, enroll students/faculty, and manage soft-skill events.\n\n2.      Faculty can enter, view, and collaboratively update marks with full audit history.\n\n3.      Students can view their marks, enrolled courses, and upcoming events.\n\n4.      Marks sheet can be downloaded as Excel (.xlsx) or uploaded to auto-populate the database.\n\n5.      Every marks update is logged — who updated it and when — visible across all faculty.\n\n## **3.1  Admin Module**\n\n### **Course Management**\n\n•        Create, edit, archive, and delete courses with metadata: title, description, credits, semester, faculty assignment.\n\n•        Enroll/un-enroll students and assign/un-assign faculty per course.\n\n•        Set course visibility (draft / published / archived).\n\n### **Soft Skill Events**\n\n•        Create events with: name, description, date/time, venue, registration deadline.\n\n•        Mark events as mandatory or optional; assign to specific batches/courses.\n\n•        Event registration list visible in admin dashboard.\n\n### **User Management**\n\n•        Bulk import students and faculty via CSV upload.\n\n•        Role assignment and account activation/deactivation.\n\n## **3.2  Faculty Module**\n\n### **Marks Entry & Collaboration**\n\n•        Select course → component (Internal/Mid-term/Final) → view student list with editable mark fields.\n\n•        Real-time save on each cell change (auto-save via debounce, 1s delay).\n\n•        All updates are attributed: 'Updated by Prof. Sharma on 14 Apr 2026 at 11:32 AM' shown inline.\n\n•        Any faculty assigned to the course can see and edit marks. Edits by one faculty are visible to all others instantly (optimistic UI + server sync).\n\n•        Marks are colour-coded: red (<35%), amber (35-49%), green (≥50%).\n\n### **Excel Operations**\n\n•        Download marks sheet as .xlsx with columns: Roll No., Name, each assessment component.\n\n•        Upload filled .xlsx → system validates structure, shows a preview diff (new vs existing), then confirms bulk import.\n\n•        Upload errors (wrong columns, out-of-range values) are listed row-by-row before import.\n\n### **Audit Log**\n\n•        Every marks change is stored: faculty_id, student_id, course_id, component, old_value, new_value, timestamp.\n\n•        Audit log viewable by all faculty of that course.\n\n## **3.3  Student Module**\n\n•        Dashboard: enrolled courses, upcoming soft-skill events, latest marks notifications.\n\n•        Marks view: per-course breakdown with component-wise marks and total/grade.\n\n•        Event registration: register/de-register for optional events.\n\n•        Download own marks card as PDF.","x":-467,"y":-160,"width":887,"height":2120},
